  "detailed_description": "Slash and dice enemies in a HEART BEAT!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2960150/extras/26c41daeda2350e27995726d06b20fc5.poster.avif?t=1759177877\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2960150/extras/26c41daeda2350e27995726d06b20fc5.webm?t=1759177877\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2960150/extras/26c41daeda2350e27995726d06b20fc5.mp4?t=1759177877\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>.<br><br>Your every click moves you around the battlefield whether it's a sword, pike, bow, or even chainsaw!<br>By clicking on the spot you will move your character demolishing every enemy between those points.<br>Shooting an arrow will move you backward while your enemies will move six feet underground!<br><br>DEFEND THE VILLAGE! Your every death will lead to demons rampaging in the city and killing civilians<br>And every win will make your city safer for new people to join!<br><br>UPGRADE YOUR GEAR! With the help of delightful Waifus in town that would love to spend time with you, and have a heart-to-heart <3",
